author: Nicki Jhabvala
title: Peyton Manning plays "Coach Gary" on ABC's Modern Family
text:
Peyton Manning had a cameo on an episode of ABC’s Modern Family that aired this week and, apparently, the two-time Super Bowl-winning quarterback has morphed into “Coach Gary,” a youth baseball coach who can play the ukulele and aspires to start his own business.
Here he is, the future owner of Gary’s Gazebos:
Peyton Manning is going into the gazebo business pic.twitter.com/G3n9wZ0X43
— A to Z Sports (@AtoZSports) February 16, 2017
